highlights.text: “กลัวว่าฉันจะไม่เสียใจ (Fear)” by PURPEECH has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 149 days straight.
“竈門炭治郎からのスペシャルメッセージ！” by アニメ『鬼滅の刃』 is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 18 spots at #61.
CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “FaSHioN” is the highest at #1.
